 "blurb": "Survival Hunter is a raid multiplier: Expose Weakness procs grant the whole melee/hunter core attack power scaled off your agility. Personal DPS is the lowest of the three trees; the raid total says otherwise, and the gear list stacks agility beyond what any other hunter would. This Phase 1 snapshot aggregates 336 top DPS parses from Karazhan, Gruul's Lair and Magtheridon; the highest-consensus pick is Beast Lord Mantle at 97% usage.",
